   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9824_qu_01.ogg}<BR>I heard an absurd rumour while you were gone. An <FONT color=#a82424>unidentified assailant</FONT> stirred up trouble at <FONT color=#086171>Abandoned Wharf</FONT> and the <FONT color=#a82424>Army of Destruction</FONT> later found out that a few of the things they were guarding went missing.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-accepting-acceptted" mid="77" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>If the rumours are true, I’m sure the <FONT color=#a82424>assailant</FONT> has fled to nearby <FONT color=#086171>Merca</FONT> to hide. Before the <FONT color=#a82424>Army of Destruction</FONT> rampages our city under the pretence of finding the assailant, I think we should act first to ensure safety of Merca. What do you think?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-1-" mid="12" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(He is inscribing rune symbols on the surface of the jewels using a carving knife. Would it really work…?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-a" mid="14" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>No one will know! Gregory sneaked them out while I attracted the guards’ attention. I’m sure no one will find out who stole them.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-b" mid="16" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9824_qu_02.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka sighs and glances at Shalica for a second.)</FONT> You’re Shalica’s <FONT color=#086171>saviour</FONT> so I won’t reproach you. But please stay low until the situation settles down.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-c" mid="18" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>All right... By the way, how’s the construction of the tower to install the relic going?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-d" mid="20" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka’s eye twitches.)</FONT> I’ve been busy sending envoys to <FONT color=#a82424>Childs in other lands</FONT> while you were busy making trouble. I didn’t have time to make a <FONT color=#086171>tower</FONT>. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-e" mid="22" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9824_qu_03.ogg}<BR>And think about it. If people realise that Merca suddenly has a new <FONT color=#086171>tower</FONT>, wouldn’t it attract suspicion? All the envoys I sent ended up dead and that is enough headache for me. It wouldn’t be a good idea to annoy the Goddess anymore.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-f" mid="24" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Then what about the relic? We got all the flawless jewels ready and we can’t install the relic…?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-g" mid="26" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9824_qu_01.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, don’t be disheartened so soon. Vernicka is not done yet. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Shalica crosses her arms as she turns to Vernicka.)</FONT> Vernicka? Stop beating about the bush and properly explain things to us now, will you?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-h" mid="28" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka scowls and bites his lips.)</FONT> …….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-i" mid="30" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(The atmosphere is too tense... I feel suffocated!)</FONT><FONT color=#662500> ……?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-j" mid="32" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9824_qu_04.ogg}<BR>Hmm... Considering all circumstances, I thought a <FONT color=#086171>tower</FONT> would stand out too much. So I thought it would be better to reconstruct the <FONT color=#086171>original structure</FONT> and create a space in it to install the relic. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-k" mid="34" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Oh, Vernicka…!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-l" mid="36" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9824_qu_05.ogg}<BR>Don’t be mistaken. I don’t have high hopes on an old relic. It’s just that I saw a <FONT color=#086171>tiny possibility</FONT> and didn’t want to ignore it. I can’t stand losing our city without a fight. Those who <FONT color=#a82424>threaten Merca</FONT> will pay a price, and that applies to the <FONT color=#a82424>Goddess</FONT> as well.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-m" mid="38" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Thank you so much....</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-n" mid="40" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Enough with that. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka turns his head.)</FONT> I’ve made it possible for the <FONT color=#086171>relic</FONT> to be installed under the <FONT color=#a82424>hourglass</FONT> in the town square so go there and try it out.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-o" mid="42" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Before that… I have a favour to ask of you, Shalica. Won’t you come with me to install the relic?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-p" mid="44" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9824_qu_02.ogg}<BR>Me…? You want me to install the relic?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-q" mid="46" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>It’s you who worked so hard to find it to save Merca. I think it’s only right that you finish what you started.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-1-r" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9824_qu_03.ogg}<BR>I thought it would of course be you who’s going to install the <FONT color=#086171>relic</FONT>. If it wasn’t for you, we wouldn’t have found it. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(A smile appears on her face.)</FONT> But I’m glad you asked me to come. <FONT color=#086171>Vernicka</FONT><FONT color=#2b2723>,</FONT><FONT color=#a82424> </FONT>do you want to come too?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-1-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-2" mid="50" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9824_qu_06.ogg}<BR>You go ahead. I’m the leader of this city and I need to stay here to protect it. I will keep my place.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2585_vernicka-2" image="QN_Nophee.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_Salica.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2585_vernicka-2-" mid="52" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica${sound:npc_Salica_9824_qu_04.ogg}<BR>Okay. You can stay here and watch how the <FONT color=#086171>tiny chance</FONT> you took can shine upon us as a bright future. Let’s go, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.<BR><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Go back to </FONT><FONT color=#086171>Norfe</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> who’s waiting for the news.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-a" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe${sound:npc_Nophee_9824_qu_01.ogg}<BR>I finished inscribing all the jewels. All we need to do now is to install these at the right place. Has <FONT color=#086171>Vernicka</FONT> prepared a <FONT color=#a82424>location</FONT> yet?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-b" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>He said we can install it under the hourglass at the town square.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2253_nophee-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Nophee.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2253_nophee-2-" mid="58" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Norfe$<BR>I knew we could trust <FONT color=#086171>Vernicka</FONT> on this. He has prepared it just at the right time. I’ll go there first and install the jewels inside the device.<BR><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>* Go to the </FONT><FONT color=#086171>hourglass</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> at the town square.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2577_salica-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2577_salica-3-a" mid="60" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Shalica is staring at the sky, looking serious with her lips tightly sealed. It’s unlikely of her to be so nervous.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2577_salica-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2577_salica-3-b" mid="62" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Completed$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2577_salica-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
